Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma lunges forward attempting to force her blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. She is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma’s sword grazes the exterior plate. She is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The path is blocked by a deep puddle of dirty sludge, there is a rope on the other side of the puddle. The adventures would need to not hesitate to make it across to avoid getting stuck.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi swims across the puddle to throw the rope across.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi was able to make it across the puddle. She passes over the rope.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Yuxi hesitates too much and manages to get stuck in the sludge. She makes it across but loses some valuables from the belt in the process.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The room begins to fill with toxic gas and there is a keyhole next to the door leading to the next chamber. Writing on the wall suggests the key seems to be in the stomach of a cow corpse next to the door.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma is able to find the key quickly. She is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. She suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi tries to climb on the salamander’s back and wrestle it into a choke hold.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. She is unharmed in the encounter.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Yuxi’s arm. She takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi attempts to rely on her intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. She is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Yuxi repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. She loses some valuables from her pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>An ogre emerges from a lift in the center of the room
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma leaps at the ogre, trying to land a killing blow.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma stabs the ogre in the chest, killing it instantly. She is met by roaring applause from the audience watching from above.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma stabs the ogre in the chest but fails to kill it instantly. She is bashed by the ogre’s fist dealing damage before it bleeds to death.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>In the following chamber there is an open treasure chest containing gold coins. The chest is also filled with crawling roaches and maggots.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi wades through the chest to grab some of the treasure.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi is not fazed by the disgusting chest. She finds a considerable amount of gold.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Yuxi reaches for the chest of coins with bugs. She is grossed out and only manages to grab a small handful of coins.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma tries to rely on her intelligence to open the box.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma was able to successfully open the box finding a valuable gemstone. She adds the gemstone to her pack.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: After too many failed attempts, the box explodes in Emma’s hand. She suffers damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A ditch of dense noxious gas separates the entrance and exit of this chamber. On the entrance wall is a riddle.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma attempts to use her wit to solve the riddle.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma announces her answer and a vent expels the gas. She waits for the gas to dissipate before proceeding.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma announces her answer and nothing happens. She runs across and suffers damage before pulling a lever dissipating the gas.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>There is a wall that has a secret rune engraved on it. However, it is also caked in smelly muck.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma tries to clean enough muck off the wall to see the rune.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma was able to tolerate the smell and cleans off enough for the rune and the walls begin to glow, revealing to her that there are gemstones along the far wall.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma tries cleaning off the rune but can’t stomach it for long. She takes a small amount of poison damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma lunges forward attempting to force her blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. She is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma’s sword grazes the exterior plate. She is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma is able to find the key quickly. She is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. She suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. She is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma’s sword grazes the exterior plate. She is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The path is blocked by a deep puddle of dirty sludge, there is a rope on the other side of the puddle. The adventures would need to not hesitate to make it across to avoid getting stuck.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi swims across the puddle to throw the rope across.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi was able to make it across the puddle. She passes over the rope.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Yuxi hesitates too much and manages to get stuck in the sludge. She makes it across but loses some valuables from the belt in the process.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The room begins to fill with toxic gas and there is a keyhole next to the door leading to the next chamber. Writing on the wall suggests the key seems to be in the stomach of a cow corpse next to the door.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma is able to find the key quickly. She is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. She suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi tries to climb on the salamander’s back and wrestle it into a choke hold.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. She is unharmed in the encounter.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Yuxi’s arm. She takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Yuxi attempts to rely on her intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. She is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Yuxi repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. She loses some valuables from her pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>An ogre emerges from a lift in the center of the room
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma leaps at the ogre, trying to land a killing blow.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma stabs the ogre in the chest, killing it instantly. She is met by roaring applause from the audience watching from above.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma stabs the ogre in the chest but fails to kill it instantly. She is bashed by the ogre’s fist dealing damage before it bleeds to death.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A ditch of dense noxious gas separates the entrance and exit of this chamber. On the entrance wall is a riddle.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma attempts to use her wit to solve the riddle.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma announces her answer and a vent expels the gas. She waits for the gas to dissipate before proceeding.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma announces her answer and nothing happens. She runs across and suffers damage before pulling a lever dissipating the gas.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma tries cleaning off the rune but can’t stomach it for long. She takes a small amount of poison damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma lunges forward attempting to force her blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. She is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma’s sword grazes the exterior plate. She is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The room begins to fill with toxic gas and there is a keyhole next to the door leading to the next chamber. Writing on the wall suggests the key seems to be in the stomach of a cow corpse next to the door.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma is able to find the key quickly. She is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. She suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Yuxi correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. She is showered by applause from the crowd.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Emma lunges forward attempting to force her blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Emma’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. She is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma’s sword grazes the exterior plate. She is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Emma hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. She suffers damage due to gas inhalation.
